message.content: The paper belongs to the arXiv CS sub-category "Information Retrieval" (cs.IR) as it presents a novel approach for retrieving information to answer complex open-domain multi-hop questions. Other likely sub-categories could include "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI), "Natural Language Processing" (cs.CL), "Machine Learning" (cs.LG), and "Data Structures and Algorithms" (cs.DS) as these fields are closely related to the topic of question answering and information retrieval.
